<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 1em;">
    <p>
      <%= @gather.user.name %> invited <%= @to_invitees %> to:
    </p>
    <h2><%= link_to @gather.activity, @url, {:style => 'background: rgba(23,129,251,1); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-bottom: 4px solid #0D509E; border-radius: 3px; font-family: helvetica; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2.5em;'} %>
    </h2> 
    <p>   
      This will only take off if at least <%= @gather.tilt %> of <%= @gather.num_invited %> friends invited join. 
      If you're interested in the activity, <b><%= link_to "join on Bloon", @url %> or text 'Y<%= @invitation.id %>' to <a href=<%="sms:"+ENV['TWILIO_MAIN'].sub('+1',"").unpack('A3A3A4').join('-')%>> <%= ENV['TWILIO_MAIN'].sub('+1',"").unpack('A3A3A4').join('-') %></a></b> so we can notify you if this activity takes off.
      <br>
      <br>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#8212;
      <br>
      Organized via Bloon. <%= link_to "Join", @url %> <%= @gather.user.name.split(' ').first %> on Bloon and effortlessly organize more fun with friends.
    </p>
    <p><small>
      Note: Your cell number will receive text messages to notify you of invitations and to organize activities with friends.
    </small></p>
  </body>
</html>
